Authorisation Bypass in Azure Portal:
 Microsoft Reply:
This is not considered a security issue, but a part of the design for your account membership. The user cannot take any privileged action on any of the directories. If you can provide more information and a PoC on this, we will be happy to service this.
You can disclose this information. Please let me know if you have any questions.


